message: "If you use KUDS in research, please cite this repository and report the exact notebook / pipeline version."
title: "KUDS: Controlled Divergence and Selection for LLM Idea Generation"
version: "v0.1"
type: software
authors:
  - name: "A.Abdulkarimova"
repository-code: "https://github.com/marieabdlk-art/kuds"
license: "MIT"
abstract: >
  KUDS is a research framework for novelty-oriented idea generation with LLMs.
  It treats ideation as a search-and-selection process rather than one-shot prompting.
keywords:
  - llm
  - idea-generation
  - novelty-search
  - prompt-engineering
  - evaluation
  - research-framework
date-released: 2026-04-07
